---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - CloudBlog" description="Learn more about CloudBlog">
  <div class="about-page">
    <h1>About CloudBlog</h1>
    
    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Built with Modern Technologies</h2>
      <p>
        CloudBlog is a modern, serverless blog platform built with cutting-edge technologies
        to deliver exceptional performance and developer experience.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
      <div class="tech-grid">
        <div class="tech-card">
          <h3>‚ö° Astro</h3>
          <p>Lightning-fast static site generator with server-side rendering capabilities</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-card">
          <h3>‚òÅÔ∏è Cloudflare Workers</h3>
          <p>Edge computing platform for blazing-fast global performance</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-card">
          <h3>üóÑÔ∏è Cloudflare D1</h3>
          <p>Distributed SQL database for storing blog posts and metadata</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-card">
          <h3>üì¶ Cloudflare R2</h3>
          <p>Object storage for images and media files with zero egress fees</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul class="features-list">
        <li>Server-side rendered blog posts with dynamic content</li>
        <li>SQL database for structured blog data</li>
        <li>Image storage with R2 object storage</li>
        <li>RESTful API for post management</li>
        <li>Tag system for content organization</li>
        <li>Comment system (can be enabled)</li>
        <li>View counter for posts</li>
        <li>Responsive, modern UI design</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <p>
        Check out the README.md file in the repository for detailed setup instructions,
        including how to configure your Cloudflare account, create databases, and deploy
        your blog to production.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-section {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-section p {
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .tech-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .tech-card {
    background: #f9fafb;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tech-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tech-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .features-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    position: relative;
    color: #4b5563;
  }

  .features-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .features-list li::before {
    content: "‚úì";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #10b981;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
